attachments.title: Wu-Tang Beer "Ain't Nothing To Funk With"
attachments.text: Philly-based brewery Dock Street Beers has a scheme to bring the rugged and raw to your next brew with a Wu-Tang-inspired beverage.
attachments.fallback: Okayplayer: Wu-Tang Beer "Ain't Nothing To Funk With"

text: Dock St brewing company in Philly is making a beer that's fermented to the tunes of Wu-Tang classics
they hope to turn it into a regular thing, and they want to do the next one with Run The Jewels
